window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Out of a room full of women, his eyes lock on mine.</p> <p>The muscled dancer is agile and skilled, and my gaze hungrily follows every teasing move. When he steps off the stage to stalk toward me, a shiver ripples down my spine.</p> <p>I've never had such an intense reaction to a guy before, especially not a stranger. But this is a tall, dark fantasy brought to life-one with a mischievous grin and chiseled abs.</p> <p>When he grips my hips, a thrilling rush courses through me, and I lose all ability to think logically. That's why I accept his invitation to grab a drink after the show.</p> <p>My adrenaline spikes further with each low whisper in my ear, until my lips find his in a searing kiss. With the wild energy of Sin City swirling around us, we float up to the privacy of a hotel room. We agree to one blissful night-that's all we can have, even if I hate the thought of never seeing him again.</p> <p>But Sebastian's an exotic dancer for Vegas's hottest male revue show. How could he be my forever?</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
